txt.en: You have become a proficient Journeyman Woodworker! You may now use Expert Woodworker recipes, or continue to work towards Journeyman Woodworker mastery.\n\nAdditionally, you are now eligible to join the <rgb=#00FF00>Woodworker's Guild</rgb>, a special reputation faction open only to Expert Woodworkers. To join the Woodworker's Guild, seek out a Master or Mistress of Crafting Guilds.
